LARAMIE , Wyo . 
( AP ) -- One of two men arrested in the beating death of gay college student Matthew Shepard merely watched while the other man pistol-whipped Shepard and left him to die , a defense attorney said Wednesday as jury selection began . 
Russell Henderson , 21 , is accused of posing as a homosexual to lure the 5-foot-2 , 105-pound Shepard out of a bar Oct. 6 . 
Opening statements were scheduled for April 6 . 
Both men could get the death penalty . 
The University of Wyoming student died five days later . 